{"tid":430511,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［心事台］成日逼自己好辛苦","createTime":"2017-10-10T00:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T01:54:53.000Z","uid":124072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f36e635a35eeed8d34b83cf1a7a4ee73d4cd23","tid":430511,"uid":124072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T00:34:50.000Z","msg":"日日都係咁逼自己溫書打好啲波<br />\n持續左好耐 好鬼辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前打波好開心 因為冇咩大目標<br />\n但宜家打到有啲pro 就有大目標<br />\n日日逼自己去練波 冇曬當時鍾意打波嘅衝勁同享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n練得唔好成日又唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀書方面就幾好 但係又係啲大目標搞到好大壓力<br />\n跟住又係咁逼自己學野 冇俾自己停<br />\n好想俾自己休息下 但係停唔到<br />\n一停落黎就係咁諗住啲目標 <br />\n就算聽緊歌睇緊戲 所謂放鬆緊<br />\n都好似放鬆唔到 好攰 好大壓力<br />\n有冇人好似我咁 同埋有冇人有咩方法解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b52dec53e36f9ff3296db49d1a339d9638a76d3","tid":430511,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T00:50:03.000Z","msg":"世上總要有失敗既廢人"},{"pid":"6b2c69432b488b7ff642b9dccaa661a97503bb77","tid":430511,"uid":124072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T01:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>世上總要有失敗既廢人</blockquote><br />\n此話何解"},{"pid":"3f95cdc737020f4d1d42eb346091aeb22a73c58a","tid":430511,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T01:47:05.000Z","msg":"我覺得你反而逼得自己太勁<br />\n練少d波啦,欲速則不達<br />\n你練波既時候 放多d心機係個技巧到仲好啦"},{"pid":"c948eb3c4066102b5d1a2d4a0b0a64fea1018cad","tid":430511,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T01:48:57.000Z","msg":"仲有可能個目標set得太高啦<br />\n本身係hea底既人你根本能力不足以應付個目標"},{"pid":"396d9bf99f85deb63900f36a45728c0f9f80d3ae","tid":430511,"uid":94069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T01:54:53.000Z","msg":"你放棄嘅話過幾年諗返會好後悔<br />\n唔想後悔就繼續"}]}